♪ May the good Lord
bless and keep you

52:55.400 --> 53:00.710
♪ Whether near or far away

53:00.760 --> 53:05.510
♪ May you find that long awaited

53:05.560 --> 53:10.350
♪ Golden day today

53:10.400 --> 53:16.310
♪ May your troubles all be small ones

53:16.360 --> 53:20.990
♪ And your fortunes ten times ten

53:21.040 --> 53:26.190
♪ May the good Lord bless
and keep you

53:26.240 --> 53:31.280
♪ Till we meet again

53:32.560 --> 53:36.750
♪ May you walk with sunlight shining

53:36.800 --> 53:41.950
♪ And a bluebird in every tree

53:42.000 --> 53:46.990
♪ May there be a silver lining

53:47.040 --> 53:52.590
♪ Back on every cloud you see

53:52.640 --> 53:58.190
♪ Fill your dreams with
sweet tomorrows

53:58.240 --> 54:03.470
♪ Never mind what might have been

54:03.520 --> 54:09.110
♪ May the good Lord bless
